<div class="about-page">

  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-visual">
      <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AppaaThe/Rituel-store@main/product-images/pg-page-hero-about.png" alt="Woman in white linen robe practicing the BY RITUEL morning ritual with an amethyst gua sha" loading="eager">
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="about-title">We built BY RITUEL because every skincare brand was selling <em>hope.</em></h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-body">

    <div class="about-block reveal">
      <p>Most skincare is passive. You apply something, you wait, and you wonder if it's working. Serums, creams, masks — they sit on your skin and rely entirely on absorption.</p>
      <p>We found something different.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-pull-quote reveal">
      "Gua sha is a practice that's been used in East Asian medicine for thousands of years. It works because it <em>moves.</em>"
    </div>

    <div class="about-block reveal">
      <p>It physically stimulates your lymphatic system, drains puffiness, boosts circulation, and sculpts your facial muscles through consistent daily movement. The ice roller seals everything in. Together, they create a ritual that produces visible results — starting from the very first morning.</p>
      <p>The problem was the market. Gua sha tools were either sold as cheap novelties with no instruction, or as overpriced clinical tools with no soul. Nobody was selling the ritual — the experience of 5 intentional minutes every morning that change not just how your skin looks, but how you start your day.</p>
      <p>That's what BY RITUEL is.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-values reveal">
      <div class="about-value">
        <span class="about-value-number">01</span>
        <h3>Five minutes, every morning.</h3>
        <p>Your morning routine should feel like something. Not a checklist. Not a transaction. A ritual — five minutes that belong entirely to you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value">
        <span class="about-value-number">02</span>
        <h3>Results you can see.</h3>
        <p>We don't sell hope. We sell a practice that physically changes your skin through consistent, intentional movement. The results are real and they're cumulative.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value">
        <span class="about-value-number">03</span>
        <h3>Premium, without pretension.</h3>
        <p>Our tools are carved from natural amethyst crystal. Our packaging feels like a luxury purchase — because showing up for yourself every day deserves that.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-block reveal">
      <p>We believe your morning routine should feel like something. Not a checklist. Not a transaction. A ritual — five minutes that belong entirely to you, that you do for yourself, every day.</p>
      <p>We're glad you found us.</p>
      <p class="about-signature">— The BY RITUEL Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-stat-row reveal">
      <div class="about-stat">
        <div class="about-stat-number">100%</div>
        <div class="about-stat-label">Natural amethyst</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat">
        <div class="about-stat-number">🌍</div>
        <div class="about-stat-label">Worldwide shipping</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat">
        <div class="about-stat-number">5 min</div>
        <div class="about-stat-label">Every morning</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat">
        <div class="about-stat-number">Day 1</div>
        <div class="about-stat-label">Visible results</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="about-cta-section">
    <span class="section-label">Ready?</span>
    <h2 class="about-cta-title">Start your ritual <em>today.</em></h2>
    <a href="{{ routes.collections_url }}/all" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;max-width:280px;text-decoration:none;text-align:center;padding:20px 48px;margin-top:40px;">
      <span>Shop the Ritual</span>
    </a>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
.about-page { overflow: hidden; }

/* Hero */
.about-hero {
  min-height: 90vh;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  padding-top: 100px;
}
.about-hero-visual {
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 500px;
  background: var(--cream-dark);
}
.about-hero-visual img {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
}
.about-hero-visual::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(30,18,10,0) 60%, rgba(30,18,10,0.18) 100%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.about-hero-content {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  padding: 80px 80px 80px 72px;
}
.about-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 58px);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-top: 20px;
}
.about-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--terracotta); }

/* Body */
.about-body { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 80px; }
.about-block p {
  font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.95; color: var(--stone);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.about-block p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.about-block { margin-bottom: 64px; }

.about-pull-quote {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
  line-height: 1.4;
  color: var(--espresso);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--terracotta);
  padding: 8px 0 8px 40px;
  margin: 64px 0;
  font-style: italic;
}
.about-pull-quote em { color: var(--terracotta); font-style: normal; }

/* Values */
.about-values {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
  margin: 64px -80px;
}
.about-value {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 48px 36px;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}
.about-value:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); }
.about-value-number {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 48px;
  color: var(--cream-dark);
  font-weight: 300;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1;
}
.about-value h3 {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.about-value p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--stone); }

.about-signature {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 20px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  margin-top: 8px;
}

/* Stats */
.about-stat-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
  margin: 64px -80px 0;
  background: var(--espresso);
}
.about-stat {
  padding: 48px 36px;
  text-align: center;
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.about-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
.about-stat-number {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 48px;
  color: var(--cream);
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.about-stat-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terracotta-light);
}

/* CTA */
.about-cta-section {
  background:
    linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(184,112,74,0.88) 0%, rgba(139,74,42,0.92) 100%),
    url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AppaaThe/Rituel-store@main/product-images/pg-page-hero-contact.png');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  padding: 120px 80px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.about-cta-section::before {
  content: 'BY RITUEL';
  position: absolute;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 260px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  top: 50%; left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  white-space: nowrap;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.about-cta-section .section-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.about-cta-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: white;
  margin-top: 16px;
  position: relative;
}
.about-cta-title em { font-style: italic; }

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .about-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-hero-visual { height: 50vh; min-height: 300px; }
  .about-hero-content { padding: 60px 40px; }
  .about-body { padding: 80px 40px; }
  .about-values { grid-template-columns: 1fr; margin: 64px 0; }
  .about-stat-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; margin: 64px 0 0; }
  .about-cta-section { padding: 80px 40px; }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Page",
  "presets": [{ "name": "About Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
